{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be vibrant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Design Studio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077cc, #00aaff);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 119, 204, 0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 3rem auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #0077cc;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #eaf4fc;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 1px solid #cce0f0;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20p